22
00:02:42,860 --> 00:02:43,450
What about you?

23
00:02:43,510 --> 00:02:44,540
I'm walking back now.

24
00:02:45,630 --> 00:02:47,140
Today's class was really difficult.

25
00:02:48,020 --> 00:02:49,670
I wish you were by my side.

26
00:02:49,670 --> 00:02:52,020
This way,
I don't have to pay attention.

27
00:02:52,420 --> 00:02:54,230
You'll give me extra lessons
anyway, right?

28
00:02:58,050 --> 00:03:00,010
Is that thing on your desk
a wedding invitation?

29
