Someone wants me
to attend their wedding,

30
00:03:07,390 --> 00:03:08,510
but I don't want to go.

31
00:03:09,070 --> 00:03:09,670
Why?

32
00:03:10,750 --> 00:03:12,910
No reason. I just don't want to go.

33
00:03:13,260 --> 00:03:14,700
You can go and have a look.

34
00:03:15,420 --> 00:03:16,470
Gain some experience.

35
00:03:16,630 --> 00:03:18,910
This way, it'll be much easier

36
00:03:19,230 --> 00:03:20,470
when we get married.

37
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:25,050
What's the matter?

38
00:03:26,100 --> 00:03:28,910
Nothing, I'm just
a little tired from class.

39
00:03:29,510 --> 00:03:31,790
I'll call you back later.

40
00:03:32,950 --> 00:03:33,510
Okay.

