=Episode 18=
(I've always been waiting for you here.)

42
00:04:08,090 --> 00:04:10,810
(Year 2024)

43
00:04:14,910 --> 00:04:15,910
What's this?

44
00:04:20,580 --> 00:04:22,110
I saw you didn't eat anything,

45
00:04:22,460 --> 00:04:24,020
so I ordered wonton skin and filling

46
00:04:24,260 --> 00:04:25,460
to make you some wontons.

47
00:04:27,460 --> 00:04:28,430
I'm not hungry.

48
00:04:51,510 --> 00:04:52,340
Do you know

49
00:04:52,820 --> 00:04:55,070
that the stomach
is not only a digestive organ,

50
00:04:55,510 --> 00:04:57,190
but also an emotional organ?

51
00:04:58,070 --> 00:04:59,550
When you take good care of it,

52
00:05:00,020 --> 00:05:01,390
your mood will also improve.

53
00:05:03,820 --> 00:05:04,950
I'll go cook for you first.

54
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:07,660
You can eat it anytime you want.

55
00:05:18,020 --> 00:05:19,260
Rest first.

56
00:05:19,450 --> 00:05:20,760
I'll let you know when it's done.

57
00:05:29,220 --> 00:05:29,750
Go.

58
