59
00:06:22,450 --> 00:06:23,250
(I've seen your music variety show.)

60
00:06:23,250 --> 00:06:23,650
(I'm proud of you.)

61
00:06:23,650 --> 00:06:24,650
(Xingruo, I feel happy
that I have a brilliant daughter.)

62
00:06:24,650 --> 00:06:25,390
(Don't exhaust yourself.)

63
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:26,090
(I'll always have your back.)

64
00:06:26,090 --> 00:06:27,010
(I recently attended
an art exhibition in Germany)

65
00:06:27,010 --> 00:06:27,710
(and saw a wonderful artwork.)

66
00:06:27,710 --> 00:06:28,810
(It reminded me
of how I taught you to draw an apple.)

67
00:06:28,810 --> 00:06:30,290
(Xingruo, I'll always support you.)

68
00:06:30,290 --> 00:06:31,590
(I'm waiting for the day when
we'll be together again.)

69
00:06:31,590 --> 00:06:32,490
(Xingruo, happy new year.)

70
