359
00:25:16,070 --> 00:25:17,940
I know you're trying to comfort me

360
00:25:18,310 --> 00:25:20,310
that the dead can't be resurrected.

361
00:25:20,740 --> 00:25:21,870
I think

362
00:25:21,940 --> 00:25:24,140
it's not too late for me to do this now.

363
00:25:24,420 --> 00:25:25,270
Dear guests,

364
00:25:26,110 --> 00:25:28,270
ladies and gentlemen.

365
00:25:28,500 --> 00:25:31,980
It is with deep sorrow
that we gather here

366
00:25:32,350 --> 00:25:33,390
today

367
00:25:33,660 --> 00:25:37,140
to bid farewell
to Mr. Shen Guangyao together.

368
00:25:37,700 --> 00:25:40,900
