at the Art Students League of New York.

371
00:25:45,980 --> 00:25:48,500
He started creating artworks in 1993.

372
00:25:48,660 --> 00:25:50,310
In 1995,

373
00:25:50,500 --> 00:25:52,940
he held
his first art exhibition in New York.

374
00:25:53,830 --> 00:25:54,940
Mr. Shen Guangyao

375
00:25:55,310 --> 00:25:56,870
was deeply influenced

376
00:25:56,940 --> 00:25:58,370
