377
00:25:58,450 --> 00:26:00,030
and incorporated
his artistic characteristics

378
00:26:00,030 --> 00:26:02,310
into his own creations.

379
00:26:02,460 --> 00:26:04,350
His works use bold colors

380
00:26:04,400 --> 00:26:06,790
and are good at describing
the emotions of a certain moment.

381
00:26:07,140 --> 00:26:10,180
They have distinct
abstract expressionist characteristics.

382
00:26:10,390 --> 00:26:14,030
Next,we'll move on
to his family members' speeches.

383
00:26:14,350 --> 00:26:16,140
Let's welcome
Mr. Shen Guangyao's daughter,

384
00:26:16,660 --> 00:26:17,900
Ms. Shen Xingruo.

385
00:26:27,500 --> 00:26:28,500
My father

386
00:26:29,740 --> 00:26:31,900
