389
00:26:40,140 --> 00:26:41,420
As his daughter,

390
00:26:42,740 --> 00:26:43,980
I want to say a few words

391
00:26:44,140 --> 00:26:46,070
to my father here today.

392
00:26:49,220 --> 00:26:50,700
Actually, before today,

393
00:26:52,220 --> 00:26:54,740
I didn't get along with my father.

394
00:26:55,870 --> 00:26:57,460
We haven't contacted each other

395
00:26:57,500 --> 00:26:59,500
for many years.

396
00:27:00,550 --> 00:27:01,870
I always thought

397
00:27:02,660 --> 00:27:03,900
that our bond

398
00:27:04,500 --> 00:27:06,140
could be so weak

399
00:27:06,630 --> 00:27:08,460
that it could be ignored.

400
00:27:09,110 --> 00:27:11,630
But the moment I knew he was dead,

401
00:27:13,140 --> 00:27:14,550
I suddenly realized

402
00:27:16,110 --> 00:27:18,420
that the two of us
are tightly bound together

403
00:27:18,630 --> 00:27:20,830
in the depths of our souls.

404
00:27:21,660 --> 00:27:24,940
We have very similar personalities

405
00:27:25,740 --> 00:27:27,790
and ways of doing things.

406
00:27:28,310 --> 00:27:30,110
Whether I'll admit it,

407
00:27:30,830 --> 00:27:32,270
they all left deep marks

408
00:27:32,270 --> 00:27:34,030
on me.

409
00:27:37,310 --> 00:27:39,590
My father once said something to me.

410
00:27:40,790 --> 00:27:41,740
He said

411
00:27:42,940 --> 00:27:44,220
I'm his daughter.

412
00:27:45,500 --> 00:27:47,790
This is a fact
that can never be changed.

413
00:27:48,700 --> 00:27:50,790
I was very repelled
by this sentence at that time.

414
00:27:51,870 --> 00:27:52,980
It's only now

415
00:27:53,630 --> 00:27:55,630
that I understand
the meaning of this statement.

416
00:27:56,740 --> 00:27:58,220
I thank my father

417
00:28:00,140 --> 00:28:02,070
for giving me life.

418
00:28:03,310 --> 00:28:04,900
All the right and wrong

419
00:28:05,350 --> 00:28:06,830
have vanished.

420
00:28:07,700 --> 00:28:09,140
I hope

421
00:28:10,220 --> 00:28:12,180
he can find eternal peace here.

422
00:28:12,900 --> 00:28:13,630
Good!

423
00:28:15,140 --> 00:28:15,940
What's going on?

424
00:28:17,590 --> 00:28:18,980
Shen Guangyao?

425
00:28:19,870 --> 00:28:22,350
Xingruo, well said!

426
00:28:22,460 --> 00:28:23,740
Isn't he dead?

427
00:28:26,400 --> 00:28:27,730
- Who's this old man?
- What's going on?

428
00:28:36,870 --> 00:28:38,110
What's going on?

429
00:28:39,700 --> 00:28:40,420
I don't know.

430
00:28:48,830 --> 00:28:49,940
My daughter.

431
00:28:52,350 --> 00:28:53,140
Mr. Shen?

432
00:28:53,830 --> 00:28:54,590
Isn't he...

433
00:28:54,940 --> 00:28:55,740
What's going on?

434
00:28:55,740 --> 00:28:56,590
Shut up.

435
00:29:05,630 --> 00:29:06,500
You're all here.

436
00:29:07,700 --> 00:29:08,980
I was able

437
00:29:09,140 --> 00:29:11,220
to meet so many old friends in one day.

438
00:29:13,030 --> 00:29:14,870
I didn't hold this ceremony in vain.

439
00:29:15,940 --> 00:29:17,700
I always wondered

440
00:29:18,870 --> 00:29:21,740
what are people's comments about me

441
00:29:21,940 --> 00:29:25,420
if I left this world one day,

442
00:29:26,740 --> 00:29:29,660
so I held this farewell ceremony

443
00:29:29,900 --> 00:29:32,180
to hear what everyone have to say.

444
00:29:33,070 --> 00:29:35,310
I was supposed
to make a grand entrance

445
00:29:35,310 --> 00:29:38,590
at the end of this farewell ceremony.

446
00:29:40,590 --> 00:29:43,030
But I was particularly moved

447
00:29:45,500 --> 00:29:47,590
by what my daughter said just now.

448
00:29:49,350 --> 00:29:50,460
So I couldn't control myself

449
00:29:50,460 --> 00:29:51,660
and showed up earlier.

450
00:29:52,550 --> 00:29:53,830
I'm thankful for my daughter.

451
00:29:55,310 --> 00:29:56,030
She

452
00:29:56,900 --> 00:29:58,870
gave today's farewell ceremony

453
00:30:00,310 --> 00:30:02,420
a new meaning.

454
00:30:03,900 --> 00:30:05,460
I'm also very happy

455
00:30:06,870 --> 00:30:10,460
that she can let go
of her previous resentment

456
00:30:12,630 --> 00:30:14,940
and give me a brief new life

457
00:30:16,870 --> 00:30:18,980
in the last stage of my life.

458
00:30:19,980 --> 00:30:20,630
Xingruo.

459
00:30:23,030 --> 00:30:25,660
Thank you.

460
00:30:28,740 --> 00:30:31,070
I would also like to thank

461
00:30:31,700 --> 00:30:33,220
the owner of this resort,

462
00:30:33,220 --> 00:30:35,140
who is also my daughter's boyfriend,

463
00:30:36,220 --> 00:30:37,030
Lu Xingyan.

464
00:30:38,030 --> 00:30:41,310
He helped me

465
00:30:41,310 --> 00:30:43,220
with the whole ceremony.

466
00:30:43,900 --> 00:30:47,110
Most importantly, I want to thank him

467
00:30:47,310 --> 00:30:48,900
for creating such a rare opportunity

468
00:30:49,270 --> 00:30:52,350
for me and my daughter

469
00:30:54,070 --> 00:30:56,140
and gave me no regrets

470
00:30:58,640 --> 00:30:59,830
in the last stage of my life.

471
00:31:01,030 --> 00:31:02,550
- Good!
- Good!

472
00:31:02,630 --> 00:31:04,420
Amazing. How amazing.

473
00:31:15,870 --> 00:31:16,940
Xingruo, let me explain.

474
00:31:16,940 --> 00:31:18,900
You already knew, didn't you?

475
00:31:19,030 --> 00:31:20,870
