477
00:31:21,870 --> 00:31:22,900
Is something wrong with you?

478
00:31:22,900 --> 00:31:23,830
Don't follow me.

479
00:31:24,350 --> 00:31:25,030
Xingruo!

480
00:31:25,700 --> 00:31:26,390
Xingruo!

481
00:31:26,870 --> 00:31:27,630
Xingruo.

482
00:31:27,900 --> 00:31:29,740
Don't you have something to tell me?

483
00:31:31,140 --> 00:31:32,270
I already said

484
00:31:32,350 --> 00:31:33,830
