485
00:31:37,700 --> 00:31:38,590
I know

486
00:31:38,700 --> 00:31:40,310
I'm wrong for lying to you,

487
00:31:40,740 --> 00:31:41,500
but

488
00:31:41,500 --> 00:31:43,460
