542
00:33:18,140 --> 00:33:19,140
- Enough.
- Calm down.

543
00:33:19,140 --> 00:33:20,420
- Stop fighting. Don't use violence.
- Who are you calling Madam?

544
00:33:20,420 --> 00:33:21,550
Miss.

545
00:33:21,550 --> 00:33:22,400
- Calm down.
- Let go!

546
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:23,700
- Enough.
- Miss, calm down.

547
00:33:24,310 --> 00:33:25,940
Madam, Miss.

