553
00:34:14,310 --> 00:34:15,150
This afternoon,

554
00:34:15,670 --> 00:34:17,020
Chen Fei accidentally hit you.

555
00:34:17,460 --> 00:34:18,500
But don't worry.

556
00:34:18,830 --> 00:34:20,390
The doctor said you're fine.

557
00:34:20,650 --> 00:34:22,520
You just need to stay in the hospital
for three days.

558
00:34:28,540 --> 00:34:29,540
I'm sorry.

559
00:34:31,390 --> 00:34:32,620
It's all my fault today.

