the ceremony's setup.

567
00:35:03,790 --> 00:35:05,020
I was also shocked.

568
00:35:07,390 --> 00:35:09,830
Mr. Shen, I really can't help you.

569
00:35:10,670 --> 00:35:11,790
I can't lie to her.

570
00:35:12,710 --> 00:35:15,230
I know what you're worried about.

571
00:35:19,020 --> 00:35:20,670
I beg you.

572
00:35:21,790 --> 00:35:22,620
My health

