581
00:35:51,420 --> 00:35:53,830
When you saw me
saying those words of gratitude on stage,

582
00:35:53,830 --> 00:35:55,310
did you feel a sense of accomplishment,

583
00:35:55,310 --> 00:35:56,020
Lu Xingyan?

584
00:35:56,020 --> 00:35:57,270
No, of course not.

585
00:35:57,790 --> 00:35:59,540
You told me so much last night.

586
00:35:59,980 --> 00:36:02,830
