588
00:36:05,710 --> 00:36:07,670
Why do you think
I want to make up with him?

589
00:36:07,670 --> 00:36:09,460
Why do you think
this is a good opportunity?

590
00:36:09,460 --> 00:36:11,670
Why did you make decisions for me?

591
00:36:14,460 --> 00:36:15,270
Sorry.

592
00:36:18,230 --> 00:36:19,060
Calm down.

593
00:36:21,060 --> 00:36:22,390
I was presumptuous.

594
00:36:23,830 --> 00:36:24,870
But I think

595
00:36:25,270 --> 00:36:26,670
as adults,

596
00:36:26,790 --> 00:36:27,980
when love vanishes

597
00:36:27,980 --> 00:36:28,940
and when two people

598
00:36:28,940 --> 00:36:30,350
can't get along anymore,

599
00:36:30,830 --> 00:36:31,580
separating

600
00:36:31,580 --> 00:36:33,420
isn't a bad decision.

601
00:36:33,830 --> 00:36:35,230
If you bind two people

602
00:36:35,230 --> 00:36:36,390
who don't love each other,

603
00:36:36,670 --> 00:36:38,750
