604
00:36:39,350 --> 00:36:41,390
Just because your dad
stopped loving your mom,

605
00:36:41,790 --> 00:36:43,100
don't hate him because you think

606
00:36:43,100 --> 00:36:44,100
he's a bad person.

607
00:36:44,750 --> 00:36:46,620
It's torture for you too.

608
00:36:48,230 --> 00:36:49,710
I don't want it to trap you.

609
00:36:52,350 --> 00:36:53,150
Lu Xingyan.

610
00:36:54,460 --> 00:36:56,230
If you don't want me to hate him,

611
00:36:57,100 --> 00:36:58,580
over his dead body.

612
00:36:58,670 --> 00:36:59,460
Why?

613
00:37:00,460 --> 00:37:01,750
Why are you so stubborn?

614
00:37:01,750 --> 00:37:04,310
Because my mom didn't die of sickness.

615
00:37:04,460 --> 00:37:06,150
She was killed.

616
00:37:06,750 --> 00:37:08,670
She was killed my dad.

617
00:37:08,670 --> 00:37:10,390
Are you satisfied with this answer?

618
00:37:15,500 --> 00:37:16,540
Shen Guangyao

619
00:37:17,980 --> 00:37:19,940
is a murderer.

